summary: An ordinance relating to zoning and providing for the rezoning of an unplatted tract of land on the south side of West McGraw Street, beginning at a point 150 feet east of 32nd Avenue West and extending east along said south side a distance of 90 feet, with respect to Use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-127 and 17-90, respectively.
